Paver Patio Installationr
r
- Excavating 12 inches down - removing all debris and earth where new patio r
    structure is intendedr
- Supply and installation of geotextile separation fabric to prevent settling during r
    freeze-thaw cycles throughout season changesr
- Supply and installation of 8 inches of compacted aggregate base stone r
    material. Stone shall be compacted in 2 inche increments to maintain 85% r
    density rating and ensure most consistent compactionr
- Supply and installation of 1 inch of screened bedding sandr
- Supply and installation of ICPI approved 2 and 3/8" thick paver block materialr
- Color blend, pattern and all aesthetic details will be approved in writing prior to r
     start of this project
